"""
    Find the length of the longest substring
    without repeating characters.
    """
    if string is None:
        return 0
    dict = {}
    max_length = 0
    j = 0
    for i in range(len(string)):
        if string[i] in dict:
            j = max(dict[string[i]], j)
        dict[string[i]] = i + 1
        max_length = max(max_length, i - j + 1)
    return max_length
